Package: PTMoreR
Type: Package
Title: PTMoreR enables a motif-centric proteomic mapping and annotation of post-translational modifications across mammalian species
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Shisheng Wang
Maintainer: Shisheng Wang <shishengwang@wchscu.cn>
Description: PTMoreR is a free, user-friendly and comprehensive web software, can provide five main functions (sequence pre-alignment, blast to human sequences, motif discovery, kinase-substrate analysis, interaction plot) to help users analyze their non-human sequence data.
